ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to Lake Helen Indian Reserve No. 53A, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 8.86 hectares (21.89 acres), more or less, including mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Red Rock Indian Band as an addition to LAKE HELEN INDIAN RESERVE NO. 53A, located in the municipal Township of Nipigon approximately 120 kilometres east of Thunder Bay, Ontario.
